' I said you can present a pig, you can make a pig look pretty, but at the end, even if you put lipstick on it, it's still a pig.

00:26:17.196 --> 00:26:17.338
And I saw things like this, and that's what I said.

00:26:21.556 --> 00:26:35.360
I try not to talk about economic stuff very much, or about sports—who I see winning games, championships, things like that—because I didn't realize how many of you all would try to gamble and do things that you do.

00:26:35.360 --> 00:26:41.720
And you tell me, 'I did this, I did that.

00:26:41.720 --> 00:26:50.088
' I'm like, 'My God, why would you do that?

00:26:50.088 --> 00:27:00.674
' But you know, that's why I have to be wise in what I say because it's not financial advice.

00:27:00.674 --> 00:27:04.173
It's just my opinion.

00:27:04.173 --> 00:27:08.500
You've got a lot of immature people.

00:27:30.714 --> 00:27:31.063
People say, 'What is a sister clipboard, Brennan?

00:27:31.063 --> 00:27:40.055
Can you tell me what that means?

00:27:40.055 --> 00:27:52.100
' Somebody who is a busybody in the body of Christ, always butting into people's business.

00:27:52.416 --> 00:28:13.994
A sister clipboard is kind of like what I would call—instead of offending people because I have a lot of women named Karen on here and I don't try to be offensive—a spiritual Karen.

00:28:13.994 --> 00:28:19.200
What the world would call a Karen.

00:28:19.200 --> 00:28:23.305
I love you, Karen.

00:28:44.136 --> 00:28:44.871
I love Karens, but the world teases about the name.

00:28:44.871 --> 00:28:49.632
They call them Karens.

00:28:55.680 --> 00:28:59.864
I just decided to call you a sister clipboard instead of a Karen because I offended Karens.

00:28:59.864 --> 00:29:03.560
There's a lot of Karens that got offended about it and I got the emails.

00:29:03.560 --> 00:29:11.640
So I decided, 'Hey, we'll call you sister clipboard instead of Karen.

00:29:11.640 --> 00:29:12.783
' Okay.

00:29:12.783 --> 00:29:17.133
So that's what that came out of.

00:29:28.265 --> 00:29:28.570
I named them that because I didn't want to offend the Karens anymore.

00:29:28.570 --> 00:29:38.827
If you remember, you've got one that said the hair and all the stuff—you can picture whoever you want her to look like.

00:29:38.827 --> 00:29:45.310
If she has a bun in her hair, if she looks like whatever, I don't care.

00:29:45.310 --> 00:29:48.450
I'm not going to paint it for you.

00:30:00.074 --> 00:30:00.480
I just call them that because they're busybodies.

00:30:01.846 --> 00:30:21.840
These people that I'm talking about are busybodies and they call by the thousands to police departments after I give the word, and they think they're going to go and tell every police station around America what I've said.

00:30:22.480 --> 00:30:29.251
And you've got the FBI and everybody reaching out to me saying, 'We've heard this.

00:30:29.251 --> 00:30:33.309
' I know y'all are watching.

00:30:33.309 --> 00:30:37.113
Thank you for watching, FBI.

00:30:37.113 --> 00:30:45.320
Thank you for watching, sheriff's departments and local law enforcement, even maybe the CIA.

00:30:49.720 --> 00:31:06.040
I believe the Lord has put me in this position to pray, but we don't need Sister Karen or Sister Clipboard calling up the police department warning them about all the words.

00:31:06.040 --> 00:31:09.434
If they know, they watch.

00:31:19.880 --> 00:31:20.387
And that's why I call you clipboards, because you're always up in people's business.

00:31:20.387 --> 00:31:27.440
It's like, 'Sit down, pray, and keep yourself to yourself.

00:31:27.440 --> 00:31:31.210
' You're not helping nobody.

00:31:31.210 --> 00:31:33.595
Keyboard warrior: 'I've got to fix everything.

00:31:33.595 --> 00:31:36.880
Oh my God, what's on Facebook?

00:31:36.880 --> 00:31:40.280
' It's like chill, chill.

00:31:40.280 --> 00:31:42.050
You've got to chill.

00:31:42.050 --> 00:31:50.420
That's why I didn't say what I saw last night.

00:32:03.160 --> 00:32:03.529
And the Lord told me, 'Why didn't you say that?

00:32:03.529 --> 00:32:06.809
' I said, 'Because of the clipboards.

00:32:06.809 --> 00:32:10.220
' And he said, 'Don't fear the clipboards.

00:32:10.220 --> 00:32:11.000
Fear me.

00:32:11.000 --> 00:32:14.733
' I said, 'I get it.

00:32:14.733 --> 00:32:20.704
' So, I'll tell you what I saw last night.

00:32:20.704 --> 00:32:27.500
You want to hear what I saw last night?

00:32:27.500 --> 00:32:33.160
Why I got quiet and didn't say nothing?

00:32:33.160 --> 00:32:37.680
Because I had to process what I was seeing.

00:32:53.827 --> 00:32:54.413
I said, 'Lord, I'll fix it tomorrow.

00:32:54.413 --> 00:33:07.960
' So, who wants to hear it for the next ten minutes?

00:33:23.680 --> 00:33:24.770
And I'm going to move on.

00:33:24.770 --> 00:33:28.034
We've got to pray.

00:33:31.000 --> 00:33:31.417
All right.

00:33:31.417 --> 00:33:34.180
This is what I saw.

00:33:34.700 --> 00:33:38.507
I saw President Trump not making it.

00:33:45.422 --> 00:33:46.418
I saw an anointing of passing and President Trump didn't make his full term.

00:33:46.418 --> 00:33:47.029
Something happens.

00:33:47.029 --> 00:33:48.200
That's all I'm going to say.

00:33:51.249 --> 00:33:51.413
I saw Vice President JD Vance become president.

00:33:54.135 --> 00:33:54.309
I saw Rubio become vice president.

00:33:54.309 --> 00:33:56.769
In this, I saw the Lord said, 'Pray for them.

00:33:56.769 --> 00:33:58.840
' I heard it very clear.

00:34:08.658 --> 00:34:08.853
The Lord said you need to pray for the next that's coming.

00:34:08.853 --> 00:34:10.263
They need prayer, too.

00:34:10.263 --> 00:34:13.440
I've always focused my prayers only on Donald Trump.

00:34:13.440 --> 00:34:20.060
And as I saw this happen, I saw an event and I saw JD Vance come on the scene.

00:34:37.760 --> 00:34:38.004
When I saw this, I saw Erica Kirk again.

00:34:38.004 --> 00:34:44.240
And Erica Kirk was consoling America because of her experience with her late husband.

00:34:59.075 --> 00:34:59.350
I saw her comforting people because she had walked through the valley.

00:34:59.350 --> 00:35:01.000
It was very detailed.

00:35:16.945 --> 00:35:17.250
I saw her being like a spokesperson because Usha was not there; it was more her.

00:35:19.560 --> 00:35:21.000
I saw a man rise up beside Erica who was polished.

00:35:42.670 --> 00:35:42.880
The Lord said specifically, 'Do not be unequally yoked with unbelievers.

00:35:42.880 --> 00:35:45.330
If you marry unequally, you're opening a door.

00:35:49.560 --> 00:35:49.960
You must marry a believing believer such as yourself.

00:35:49.960 --> 00:35:53.130
' And that was to every person.

00:35:53.130 --> 00:35:57.080
Doesn't matter if they seem polished, they would help.

00:35:57.080 --> 00:36:00.547
If they ain't a Christian, don't marry them.

00:36:00.547 --> 00:36:05.577
If they're into another kind of religion, don't marry them.

00:36:05.577 --> 00:36:11.760
And I saw this was concerning JD.

00:36:19.653 --> 00:36:20.080
I warned him.

00:36:21.360 --> 00:36:25.596
The Lord said—now, do I say too much?

00:36:25.596 --> 00:36:26.129
You ask.

00:36:26.129 --> 00:36:28.673
I have nothing to hide from nobody.

00:36:53.815 --> 00:36:54.050
I tell you, and I told the Lord, I'm bold as a lion.

00:36:54.050 --> 00:37:04.377
I'll say exactly what I see and I'll tell you what's coming next in the vision.

00:37:14.290 --> 00:37:14.780
I saw patriots that were like militia and they took over the Mississippi River with airboats.

00:37:14.780 --> 00:37:21.410
They had big fans and they had AKs and they had guns that were not semi-automatic; they were automatic.

00:37:21.410 --> 00:37:24.910
I don't know where they got them, but they were military.

00:37:28.709 --> 00:37:28.966
And I saw them.

00:37:28.966 --> 00:37:35.554
They looked like bikers with vests on and they had patches all over their vests for what they were—helicopter pilots and special ops and all kinds of things.

00:37:47.093 --> 00:37:47.351
But they had patches of snakes and things on their vests.

00:37:48.945 --> 00:38:01.670
And I saw these men that had big burly beards and some of them just looked like they were bald and they were older, like my dad's age.

00:38:01.670 --> 00:38:05.870
probably in their 60s, maybe 70s, I don't know.

00:38:13.080 --> 00:38:16.227
But these men looked like they were not wanting to mess around.

00:38:16.227 --> 00:38:19.275
They were serious and they were trained killers.

00:38:29.933 --> 00:38:30.080
I was looking at these men that said, 'I have sworn to the Constitution to protect against foreign and domestic.

00:38:30.080 --> 00:38:43.300
' And I saw them rise up and they were blocking roads and they had military checkpoints and they had places of refuge of what they called like military camps.

00:38:43.300 --> 00:38:49.657
They had heavy artillery, lots of stuff, homemade explosives.

00:38:49.657 --> 00:38:55.126
I'm talking this looked like something out of a movie.

00:38:55.126 --> 00:39:00.195
But they were groups and they were set up in bases across our nation.

00:39:01.796 --> 00:39:02.067
And that's what I saw.

00:39:07.726 --> 00:39:08.651
I saw Texas secede from the nation and become its own.

00:39:11.356 --> 00:39:15.462
I saw walls, like in the spirit, dividing Texas from Louisiana and Texas from Mexico, and Oklahoma became a part of Texas.

00:39:15.462 --> 00:39:17.606
I saw they were friends.

00:39:19.725 --> 00:39:19.920
I saw crops.

00:39:33.495 --> 00:39:33.860
I saw homemade gardens, and the Lord reminded me of the book 'One Second After,' 'One Minute After,' 'One Second.

00:39:33.860 --> 00:39:36.730
' Show them the cover.

00:39:36.730 --> 00:39:45.609
And the Lord said, "This is something you need to pray about.

00:39:45.609 --> 00:39:48.432
" I saw civil war break out in our nation.

00:39:48.432 --> 00:39:49.977
I saw it divided again.

00:39:51.973 --> 00:39:53.040
I saw it was the Democrats versus the Republicans.

00:39:53.040 --> 00:39:53.680
Show them.

00:39:53.680 --> 00:39:55.240
Now, I am not promoting this book.

00:39:55.240 --> 00:40:04.025
This is what I saw in the spirit when I was praying.

00:40:04.025 --> 00:40:05.445
Okay, show them.

00:40:15.320 --> 00:40:15.520
I'm moving on.

00:40:18.937 --> 00:40:19.194
And I saw checkpoints.

00:40:27.040 --> 00:40:27.180
I saw it was like a police state, but it was not a police state.

00:40:33.034 --> 00:40:36.093
It was the local law enforcement, the sheriff's department, who had jurisdiction over the whole area, were coordinating and were working beside military people that were like Desert Storm and Iraqi Freedom.

00:40:43.009 --> 00:40:43.204
The military people that were retired were no longer retired.

00:40:43.204 --> 00:40:49.933
They were defending our own nation, foreign and domestic, as something was trying to come over our nation to take it over.

00:40:49.933 --> 00:40:51.587
Does that make sense?

00:41:00.420 --> 00:41:00.670
But it was a deep state; it was something very dark being planned.

00:41:00.670 --> 00:41:03.440
But I saw Rubio and I saw JD Vance.

00:41:09.213 --> 00:41:13.524
And the Lord said, "Pray for them.

00:41:25.013 --> 00:41:25.231
" I saw a diffusing, with a man speaking peace.

00:41:25.667 --> 00:41:47.724
I saw he was good with his mouth, and it was diffusing the people from uprising.

00:42:00.760 --> 00:42:01.006
All this was very strong.

00:42:01.006 --> 00:42:16.040
So whenever I'm seeing things, I don't know what to do with a lot of it because I'm seeing darkness.

00:42:16.040 --> 00:42:19.663
I'm seeing catastrophe and I don't know.

00:42:22.382 --> 00:42:31.423
And there's a lot of times when I'm seeing it, you say, "Well, Brandon, why don't you tell me what you're seeing at that moment?

00:42:31.423 --> 00:42:32.857
" I'm seeing it.

00:42:33.223 --> 00:42:36.595
I don't know what to do with it.

00:42:36.595 --> 00:42:41.400
All I know how to do is to pray.

00:42:41.400 --> 00:42:51.777
And I know I'm on a live camera, so I'm not afraid of what I see.

00:42:51.777 --> 00:42:54.213
I pray for our president.

00:42:54.213 --> 00:42:56.640
I pray for JD Vance.

00:42:56.640 --> 00:42:58.920
I pray for Marco Rubio.

00:42:58.920 --> 00:43:00.538
I pray for these people.

00:43:00.538 --> 00:43:12.920
But it's very real to me when I'm seeing over in the spirit and I see these military and I see these pontoon boats.

00:43:12.920 --> 00:43:13.820
I see people.

00:43:15.307 --> 00:43:16.187
And the Lord said, "One second after.

00:43:16.187 --> 00:43:24.140
" So I'm like, "Are we struck by another nation?

00:43:24.140 --> 00:43:30.780
" I want you to think about what I'm saying because I'm not going to directly say it.

00:43:32.840 --> 00:43:33.480
One second after.

00:43:33.480 --> 00:43:36.000
What is the book?

00:43:36.000 --> 00:43:37.018
What happens?

00:43:37.018 --> 00:43:38.262
Why are the trees burnt?

00:43:38.262 --> 00:43:54.080
When I said I saw JD with a trench coat on walking through these trees that look charred by something, what happened?

00:43:54.080 --> 00:43:54.907
Why?

00:43:54.907 --> 00:43:56.977
Why would that happen?

00:43:56.977 --> 00:44:02.644
Why was he there?

00:44:02.644 --> 00:44:04.012
Why was he alone?

00:44:10.000 --> 00:44:11.425
There was snow—some kind of ash all over the ground.

00:44:15.640 --> 00:44:15.824
It looked like snow.

00:44:15.824 --> 00:44:16.560
Something was wrong.

00:44:17.640 --> 00:44:18.920
And I said all the trees were bare, seven of them.

00:44:18.920 --> 00:44:23.326
There was something to this.

00:44:31.920 --> 00:44:32.138
And that's when the Lord said, "Pray for this.

00:44:32.138 --> 00:44:33.444
Pray for JD Vance.

00:44:33.444 --> 00:44:42.080
You don't pray for him enough.

00:44:42.080 --> 00:44:45.245
You don't pray for Marco Rubio.

00:44:45.245 --> 00:44:47.634
You've just been praying over Trump.

00:45:00.253 --> 00:45:00.404
" So I stopped, not knowing what to do with what I was given.

00:45:02.920 --> 00:45:03.907
And I started interceding for JD Vance and Marco Rubio.

00:45:03.907 --> 00:45:06.291
So did I do it in ten minutes?

00:45:13.103 --> 00:45:13.537
I tried.

00:45:13.537 --> 00:45:16.404
So can we stop it?

00:45:17.600 --> 00:45:17.800
I believe we could.

00:45:23.848 --> 00:45:24.120
I believe we can protect President Trump.

00:45:34.644 --> 00:45:34.769
I believe the Lord said to carry him across the finish line.

00:45:34.769 --> 00:45:36.452
But I see some kind of an event from another country.

00:45:36.452 --> 00:45:45.380
Do you remember when I told you down the Mississippi River I saw North Korea with the black and white rocket?

00:45:48.413 --> 00:45:48.867
It said USSR on the top side of it.

00:45:50.067 --> 00:45:55.320
And they were going to get oats out of something on the Mississippi River.

00:46:01.040 --> 00:46:01.910
And they shot the rocket off over that area down the Mississippi, and it said USSR on it.

00:46:04.085 --> 00:46:04.840
It was black and white.

00:46:09.240 --> 00:46:09.453
And when they did, it didn't get high enough.

00:46:11.604 --> 00:46:11.827
And I saw an EMP in the spirit.

00:46:11.827 --> 00:46:13.160
Does anybody remember that?

00:46:19.440 --> 00:46:23.096
And I said, "It went off out of the Mississippi.

00:46:26.560 --> 00:46:30.977
" And they were shooting it off over Kentucky, Tennessee, that area, but it didn't get high enough.

00:46:30.977 --> 00:46:35.130
So when it went off, it didn't affect Oklahoma.

00:46:36.270 --> 00:46:36.840
It didn't affect Texas.

00:46:38.022 --> 00:46:41.411
It didn't affect parts of Florida, but it really affected the East.

00:46:41.411 --> 00:46:44.735
These are the same visions I saw.

00:46:49.849 --> 00:46:51.180
And that's when I stopped and I said, "Am I looking into the tribulation?

00:46:51.180 --> 00:46:53.263
Surely this is not now.

00:47:06.614 --> 00:47:07.228
" I can see the tribulation being really bad in America.

00:47:07.228 --> 00:47:12.755
You know, is JD Vance here for the tribulation?

00:47:12.755 --> 00:47:15.465
Is Marco Rubio?

00:47:15.465 --> 00:47:17.493
They both say they're believers.

00:47:22.538 --> 00:47:24.275
I don't know.

00:47:32.480 --> 00:47:32.990
That's why I try to weigh everything out.

00:47:44.018 --> 00:47:44.182
I'm just real with y'all because I'm like, Marco Rubio says he's a believer.

00:48:01.560 --> 00:48:10.980
So if the rapture of the church happened, I believe Marco Rubio is going to be there.

00:48:10.980 --> 00:48:17.400
JD Vance says he loves the Lord too, so he should be going too.

00:48:17.400 --> 00:48:20.580
And then there's people, "Well, I don't believe that.

00:48:38.568 --> 00:48:38.912
" That's why I said I'm not going to argue whether or not we have a rapture or we don't.

00:48:38.912 --> 00:48:47.560
That's why I tried to be really cautious of that because there's people that come, "Brandon, you are so wrong.

00:48:47.560 --> 00:48:49.200
We're going through the whole tribulation.

00:49:02.760 --> 00:49:14.560
" I said, "Well, if you're right and we're here, then I don't see how it could be possible, but if it is and you're right, then my goodness, I hope you're ready because it's literal hell on earth.

00:49:14.560 --> 00:49:21.960
" So the things I see, I try to pinpoint: is this something we can stop?

00:49:21.960 --> 00:49:28.480
Is this something that is bound to happen?

00:49:47.304 --> 00:49:47.896
I know President Trump only has two and a half years left, right?

00:50:08.280 --> 00:50:08.625
But I didn't see him when this took place.

00:50:24.496 --> 00:50:25.032
I did not see him.

00:50:25.032 --> 00:50:27.467
He was not there.

00:50:27.467 --> 00:50:32.430
So he was gone.

00:50:32.440 --> 00:50:33.674
Something happened to him.

00:50:35.960 --> 00:50:41.415
But JD was there and Marco Rubio was there.

00:50:41.415 --> 00:50:47.400
So what does that mean?

00:50:47.747 --> 00:50:50.648
I don't want to add to, "Well, somebody did something bad to Trump.

00:51:05.620 --> 00:51:05.970
" So I started praying for his kids.

00:51:13.840 --> 00:51:14.140
I don't know.

00:51:14.140 --> 00:51:17.740
All I saw was JD Vance and Marco Rubio.

00:51:17.740 --> 00:51:26.305
So he was vice president and JD Vance was president and I saw an event, but then I heard Erica trying to console the people.

00:51:26.305 --> 00:51:29.292
So I don't know what happened.

00:51:43.600 --> 00:51:43.800
Why would she be consoling the people?

00:51:43.800 --> 00:51:44.860
What was she doing?

00:51:44.860 --> 00:51:51.840
She was on camera and she was a spokesperson and she was talking about Charlie.

00:51:52.320 --> 00:51:56.335
And so I thought it was interesting.

00:51:56.335 --> 00:52:01.157
So I just try to give you what I saw.

00:52:01.157 --> 00:52:17.741
Like I said, I have nothing to hide, but I'm going to tell you this: I pray for President Trump until the Lord assigns me to do something else.

00:52:22.920 --> 00:52:23.424
And I pray for JD Vance now.

00:52:23.424 --> 00:52:26.200
And I'm praying for Marco Rubio.

00:52:26.200 --> 00:52:28.229
And I'm praying for our nation.

00:52:28.229 --> 00:52:38.784
And I'm praying for freedom fighters or warriors, whatever they are, that they'll protect America and serve them.

00:52:38.784 --> 00:52:42.316
We have our FBI, our people.

00:52:50.760 --> 00:52:51.378
But what was interesting in this, I did not see FBI.

00:52:51.378 --> 00:52:55.173
I did not see CIA or whatever.

00:52:58.440 --> 00:52:58.880
I saw veterans.

00:52:58.880 --> 00:52:59.760
Why?

00:52:59.760 --> 00:53:03.920
Where were the other law enforcement people?

00:53:28.778 --> 00:53:28.996
I don't know, NSA.

00:53:28.996 --> 00:53:38.649
So I say this to say, that's why I'm always not quick to release it.

00:53:49.440 --> 00:53:49.623
But like I said, the Lord said to me, "Why do you hold things back sometimes?

00:53:55.840 --> 00:53:56.640
" I said, "Because of sister clipboards.

00:53:59.554 --> 00:53:59.869
I told you to pray.

00:54:00.183 --> 00:54:06.400
What you do with it is on you.

00:54:06.400 --> 00:54:09.034
It's not my responsibility to spoon-feed you.

00:54:09.034 --> 00:54:12.940
If you want to choke on it, choke on it.

00:54:12.940 --> 00:54:17.020
If you can't handle it, go watch somebody else.

00:54:17.020 --> 00:54:23.120
But I'm here to tell you, we're in a place, a time like we've never been before.

00:54:24.693 --> 00:54:29.144
And we must pray for our president and get him across the finish line.

00:54:29.144 --> 00:54:36.800
We must pray for our vice president because I hadn't been praying for him because I don't like JD Vance.

00:54:36.800 --> 00:54:39.240
I'm just being real with you.

00:54:39.680 --> 00:54:41.084
I pray for him a little.

00:54:54.320 --> 00:54:56.055
I tiptoe around it.

00:54:56.055 --> 00:55:04.160
I'm like, 'I'll pray for Trump because I really like him, but it's hard for me to like JD Vance sometimes.

00:55:04.160 --> 00:55:11.656
' I think he's kind of cocky, but you know what?

00:55:22.320 --> 00:55:22.840
I go, 'Okay, well, I'm going to pray for him.

00:55:22.840 --> 00:55:28.315
' And the Lord said, 'You don't pray for him enough.

00:55:28.730 --> 00:55:30.710
You need to pray for him.

00:55:30.710 --> 00:55:33.284
' Now, He corrected me strong last night.

00:55:43.940 --> 00:55:44.265
And He said, 'And not only pray for him, pray for Marco Rubio.

00:55:44.265 --> 00:55:54.122
' Because I saw an anointing coming on the two of them to lead the nation soon.

00:56:09.240 --> 00:56:09.560
And I thought, "What is that?

00:56:09.560 --> 00:56:13.240
" But it looked like some kind of an endowment.

00:56:13.240 --> 00:56:18.006
It looked like some kind, you know, like knighting.

00:56:25.307 --> 00:56:25.573
It was like a cloak coming on JD Vance and Marco Rubio.

00:56:27.440 --> 00:56:28.280
And I saw this thing coming on them.

00:56:28.700 --> 00:56:31.234
And the Lord said, "Pray for them.

00:56:35.240 --> 00:56:35.840
Don't wait until it happens.

00:56:35.840 --> 00:56:37.662
Do it now.

00:56:37.662 --> 00:56:38.907
Pray for him.

00:56:38.907 --> 00:56:52.350
" So that's why I did what I did last night, just letting you know.

00:56:52.360 --> 00:56:55.307
That's heavy.

00:56:55.720 --> 00:56:58.391
I feel the anointing hit me.

00:56:58.391 --> 00:57:01.170
But I'm going to tell you what else he said.

00:57:07.680 --> 00:57:08.013
He said, "There will be no one to save America other than me.

00:57:09.680 --> 00:57:17.084
" He said to me, "What's the difference between Obama and all the things that I've seen concerning Trump?

00:57:19.440 --> 00:57:22.520
" He said, "Barack Obama was the world, and the church didn't idolize Obama.

00:57:36.509 --> 00:57:39.535
" He said, "Do you remember whenever Brother Hagin and Smith Wigglesworth said the moment you start looking at them as the savior and able to fix everything, the moment they are usually removed?

00:57:40.005 --> 00:57:47.473
" And Brother Hagin said, "I always make sure I attract to deflect, to always give God praise.

00:57:47.473 --> 00:57:59.955
I always give all the glory to Jesus because as soon as people start looking at you, I know that I will be removed.

00:58:09.383 --> 00:58:09.891
" You want me to say that again?

00:58:09.891 --> 00:58:13.613
Brother Hagin knew the difference between the balance of attract to deflect.

00:58:13.613 --> 00:58:16.985
Always give Jesus the praise.

00:58:22.698 --> 00:58:23.942
The moment man keeps their eyes on you to fix or as the healer, the moment that your time is almost up on this earth, something happens.

00:58:23.942 --> 00:58:30.640
The same thing happened to Smith Wigglesworth and the articles in the paper.

00:58:30.640 --> 00:58:33.800
And he said, "Oh, poor Smith.

00:58:39.375 --> 00:58:42.560
" He told everybody the moment they started looking at me, he knew his time was done.

00:58:42.560 --> 00:58:45.457
And Smith Wigglesworth went home.

00:58:57.280 --> 00:58:57.480
He realized that he is not the source of the power.

00:58:57.680 --> 00:58:59.493
The power only flows through a vessel.

00:58:59.493 --> 00:59:05.738
And the Lord said, "I'll share my glory with no one.

00:59:18.140 --> 00:59:25.000
" And they idolize, and it's idolatry to me the way the body of Christ is looking at him.

00:59:25.000 --> 00:59:26.020
He was very stern about it.

00:59:29.360 --> 00:59:29.568
He shook me.

00:59:30.192 --> 00:59:35.100
He said, "The church, there is a perversion the way they look at Trump.

00:59:35.230 --> 00:59:36.138
The church is in perversion.

00:59:51.400 --> 00:59:51.824
It's idolatry the way they are looking at him.

00:59:55.880 --> 00:59:57.971
" And I know I'm making some of you mad as a hornet, but that's what he said.

00:59:57.971 --> 01:00:02.000
"There will be no other gods.

01:00:02.760 --> 01:00:11.480
" And he said, "Brandon, the difference between the world and Obama—how they looked at him and the way all this is going—is," he said, "You're my church.

01:00:12.351 --> 01:00:14.380
The church is a totally different thing than the world.

01:00:14.380 --> 01:00:17.592
" He said, "You're separate unto me.

01:00:17.592 --> 01:00:19.000
You're my bride.

01:00:21.560 --> 01:00:24.587
" And he said, "My bride is looking to a man and it's idolatry to fix everything.

01:00:45.978 --> 01:00:47.222
" And whenever somebody puts the pressure—when he puts a picture out and they defend him to death, "Oh, there's a healing and he has Jesus's cloak on" and all this stuff—the church is like, "Oh, he doesn't mean it.

01:00:47.222 --> 01:00:50.360
Oh, God, don't touch him.

01:00:52.955 --> 01:01:00.800
" And if I say anything, I have people throwing rocks at me or trying to hit me like Goliath and take my head at the same time.

01:01:08.040 --> 01:01:08.315
And I'm saying, I'm not trying to speak nothing.

01:01:08.315 --> 01:01:09.965
Same thing with Bibi.

01:01:17.740 --> 01:01:18.280
"You anti-semitic non-Christian man.

01:01:27.720 --> 01:01:28.073
" I said I love the Jews more than you'll ever know.

01:01:28.073 --> 01:01:30.880
It had nothing to do with it.

01:01:41.255 --> 01:01:41.510
I ain't talking trash about nobody.

01:01:41.510 --> 01:01:47.107
I'm trying to warn you what I'm hearing in the spirit that Bibi is...

01:01:47.107 --> 01:01:49.490
I saw him be taken out by an assassin.

01:01:49.490 --> 01:01:53.520
I'm trying to warn you about these things.

01:01:53.520 --> 01:02:00.030
And people think, "Well, Brandon...

01:02:00.040 --> 01:02:01.987
" and they get mad at me.

01:02:25.880 --> 01:02:26.080
I just want to keep it to myself.

01:02:29.782 --> 01:02:30.004
Why do I have to say this stuff?

01:02:30.004 --> 01:02:42.465
Because they don't have ears to hear anyway, as these people all have their heads in the sand and they're on some kind of weird crack—the way the Christians act.

01:02:42.465 --> 01:02:46.190
And they are just like Trump Derangement Syndrome.

01:02:46.190 --> 01:02:51.198
And I love Trump just as much as you all.

01:03:00.307 --> 01:03:00.596
I pray for him.

01:03:00.596 --> 01:03:05.430
But the body of Christ has a sickness about it.

01:03:05.430 --> 01:03:10.720
They act weird and there is no balance to it.

01:03:12.235 --> 01:03:14.347
And the Lord said, "It's idolatry to me the way they look at him.

01:03:15.072 --> 01:03:18.055
And I told you, I'll have no other gods before me.

01:03:19.600 --> 01:03:20.525
" And he isn't a king.

01:03:22.555 --> 01:03:22.850
He's a man.

01:03:22.850 --> 01:03:31.040
And he said, "It's not going to be popular, but you tell them what I say.

01:03:31.040 --> 01:03:39.160
" And I can tell you there's a lot of prophetic channels that—I don't want to be rude—but they are a bunch of brown-nose rear-kissers.

01:03:52.400 --> 01:03:52.829
And that's the way it is.

01:04:04.751 --> 01:04:04.969
And I'm going to tell you this: it has to stop.

01:04:16.320 --> 01:04:16.710
The only person who's going to save America is the Lord Jesus Christ.

01:04:19.498 --> 01:04:20.933
And you better put Jesus on the pedestal, not a man.

01:04:20.933 --> 01:04:25.280
He is flawed, and so are we.

01:04:43.920 --> 01:04:44.155
And there's only one person that's going to save him, and that's Jesus.

01:04:44.155 --> 01:04:50.080
He needs an awakening unto God just like every single one of us.

01:04:55.360 --> 01:04:55.547
And people have exalted a man.

01:04:57.040 --> 01:05:01.150
And the Lord said this to me: "Should I go that far?

01:05:01.160 --> 01:05:08.960
There's been a door of pride that has been opened and a great shaking to awaken.

01:05:24.312 --> 01:05:24.736
For the bride will be brought back to my side.

01:05:24.736 --> 01:05:26.204
For I am coming.

01:05:43.320 --> 01:05:43.520
A wound that will not be fatal in the days ahead.

01:05:43.520 --> 01:05:45.406
" That's what he said.

01:05:52.065 --> 01:05:52.240
A shaking across this world.

01:05:52.240 --> 01:05:53.200
A shaking.

01:05:53.200 --> 01:05:56.040
And I saw the headlines and newspapers.

01:06:04.540 --> 01:06:04.760
I saw the headlines and things that I saw coming.

01:06:18.832 --> 01:06:19.024
And the Lord—I'm not going to say all of what I saw.

01:06:23.853 --> 01:06:24.167
And the Lord said, "This is why I told the church to pray.

01:06:24.167 --> 01:06:25.580
" But he shook me.

01:06:25.580 --> 01:06:27.577
So if you want to unsubscribe, bye.

01:06:27.577 --> 01:06:29.360
I told you, pray for the man.

01:06:29.360 --> 01:06:30.594
Pray for him.

01:06:30.594 --> 01:06:35.400
But there will be no other gods before our God.

01:06:43.531 --> 01:06:43.794
And there will be no church that looks to a man to save anything other than the Lord Jesus Christ.

01:06:43.794 --> 01:06:47.200
He can use him, but you don't idolize him.

01:06:47.200 --> 01:06:51.686
He will use me, but you don't idolize me.

01:06:55.200 --> 01:06:55.510
You don't idolize Kathryn Kuhlman.

01:06:56.750 --> 01:06:57.370
You don't idolize whoever.

01:07:00.840 --> 01:07:03.531
You look to Jesus Christ because he is the one that's in control.

01:07:03.531 --> 01:07:05.840
I decrease that he increase.

01:07:08.160 --> 01:07:16.910
And the moment you increase and you start looking at yourself like you're Jesus Christ and putting photos that way, you've opened a major door and you can defend them all you want to.

01:07:16.910 --> 01:07:21.200
He said it was the root of the heart.

01:07:21.200 --> 01:07:24.185
It's the root and what is being displayed from the heart.

01:07:34.190 --> 01:07:34.480
What do you see?

01:07:34.480 --> 01:07:41.623
What do I see that you don't see?

01:07:41.623 --> 01:07:43.109
He said, "Pray.

01:07:44.070 --> 01:07:53.020
" So, it's not always easy being Brandon Biggs telling you what I hear, but I tell you with the fear of the Lord.

01:07:53.545 --> 01:07:55.387
And I tell you, look to Jesus.

01:07:55.387 --> 01:07:59.240
He's the only one that's ever going to fix everything you need.

01:07:59.240 --> 01:08:07.840
He's the only one that can fix your economy.

01:08:07.840 --> 01:08:14.320
Whenever the economy goes down and America will be humbled in the days ahead, America will be humbled.

01:08:16.350 --> 01:08:18.658
And that's probably not a real popular message, but I saw it.

01:08:23.160 --> 01:08:23.480
I saw shaking.

01:08:23.800 --> 01:08:24.580
I saw shaking.

01:08:24.580 --> 01:08:27.040
Lord said, "Pray for President Trump.

01:08:27.040 --> 01:08:29.120
Pray for his kids.

01:08:29.120 --> 01:08:30.880
Pray for his family.

01:08:30.880 --> 01:08:35.740
" So I continue to do it.

01:08:35.740 --> 01:08:48.946
But if the church would stop idolizing people—we don't have a king, we have a president.

01:09:04.805 --> 01:09:05.000
And it's the way the people look at him as a king; it's idolatry.

01:09:08.510 --> 01:09:09.326
And that's what the Lord was showing me: "I am the King.

01:09:09.326 --> 01:09:12.044
There will be no other before me.

01:09:14.324 --> 01:09:14.660
" And you say, "Well, that's not me.

01:09:14.660 --> 01:09:18.935
" Well, then I'm not talking to you.

01:09:18.935 --> 01:09:21.400
But there's millions of them that are.

01:09:21.400 --> 01:09:22.799
"I'm on the Trump train.

01:09:31.175 --> 01:09:31.430
" I love him with all my heart.

01:09:47.940 --> 01:09:48.240
I think he's a great guy.

01:09:48.240 --> 01:09:51.540
I'm sure I'd love to meet him one day.

01:09:51.540 --> 01:09:56.190
I don't know if he'd want to meet me, but I'd meet him.

01:09:56.190 --> 01:09:57.830
Pray for him all the time.

01:09:57.830 --> 01:10:12.453
But to be on the Trump Train and MAGA and to always think the things that we think because we're so leftist or right and all this, let's just go down the middle and say we're for Jesus.

01:10:22.526 --> 01:10:22.880
I don't claim a political party.

01:10:22.880 --> 01:10:24.347
I'm not red.

01:10:24.347 --> 01:10:25.787
I'm not blue.

01:10:29.411 --> 01:10:29.737
I vote Republican every single time.

01:10:29.737 --> 01:10:52.840
But I'm going to tell you this, for the corruption that I have seen on both sides concerning why we have a young man in California trying to have bills passed against him—if you say anything against the corruption in California and they're wanting to give you a $10,000 fine, and Elon Musk is talking about it because Nick Shirley's trying his best to expose it.

01:10:52.840 --> 01:10:56.493
I said, "Why are the Republicans not doing this?

01:10:56.493 --> 01:10:59.185
" Because there's corruption among the Republicans.

01:10:59.185 --> 01:11:02.114
There are Republicans on the Democrat side.

01:11:02.114 --> 01:11:03.674
They're both bad.

01:11:06.540 --> 01:11:07.540
And the Lord said, "You must pray.

01:11:22.120 --> 01:11:22.507
" But make sure he's doing his best.

01:11:22.507 --> 01:11:25.790
I told you, pray for that man's safety.

01:11:26.240 --> 01:11:27.253
Pray for his safety.

01:11:27.253 --> 01:11:36.200
I've seen it more than once now: him being taken out by some deranged idiot on the side trying to hurt this kid.

01:11:38.631 --> 01:11:38.836
And the Lord said, "Pray for him.

01:11:38.836 --> 01:11:41.709
He's more violent than even a Charlie Kirk.

01:11:41.709 --> 01:11:51.520
" And it's sad to me, you know, he's probably doing it because he loves our nation or whatever, but it shouldn't be him, right?

01:11:51.520 --> 01:11:53.320
Or should it be?

01:11:53.320 --> 01:11:54.760
Where's Pam Bondi at?

01:11:54.760 --> 01:11:55.504
She's fired.

01:11:59.293 --> 01:11:59.547
A new one's coming in, right?

01:12:09.600 --> 01:12:09.960
I just tell you this out of love.

01:12:09.960 --> 01:12:15.450
I'm not trying to be mean.

01:12:15.450 --> 01:12:26.194
I'm trying to tell you what I heard, and there was a lot more to what he said, but I try to warn you.

01:12:26.194 --> 01:12:28.535
So, throw rocks at me.

01:12:28.535 --> 01:12:30.231
Tell me Brandon's a false prophet.

01:12:30.231 --> 01:12:30.613
Whatever.

01:12:30.613 --> 01:12:31.187
I did the best I can.

01:12:31.187 --> 01:12:34.091
Jeremiah had a hard too, right?

01:12:47.525 --> 01:12:47.830
And the Lord said, "Speak the hard things.

01:12:47.830 --> 01:12:50.432
Tell them what's coming.

01:12:56.390 --> 01:12:56.585
Pray.

01:12:56.585 --> 01:12:57.170
Pray more.

01:12:57.170 --> 01:13:00.200
Stop looking at him the way we do.

01:13:00.200 --> 01:13:02.580
" All right, let's pray.

01:13:05.949 --> 01:13:08.280
That was not easy, but I told the Lord I'd do it today.

01:13:08.280 --> 01:13:10.485
I said, "I'll do it.

01:13:10.485 --> 01:13:12.220
I'll say it.

01:13:12.220 --> 01:13:26.360
Regardless of whether Paula White says what she says or whoever says what they say, he may have gone through a hard time, but he didn't go through anything like Jesus Christ did.

01:13:26.360 --> 01:13:41.880
Just to let you know, the Lord allowed me to see His crucifixion and I saw what He went through and it was the most gruesome death I can ever describe to you.

01:13:50.743 --> 01:13:51.017
" And He said, "Brandon, I suffered greatly for every single one of them, that none of them should perish, but all come to repentance.

01:13:51.017 --> 01:13:52.143
I suffered greatly.

01:13:52.143 --> 01:13:53.354
" Do you understand?

01:13:53.354 --> 01:14:00.074
"I suffered so that they don't have to have sickness and disease.

01:14:00.074 --> 01:14:06.400
I suffered so that they don't have to be poor.

01:14:06.400 --> 01:14:14.609
I suffered so that they could come with me and be with me in paradise forever.

01:14:14.609 --> 01:14:17.360
" He allowed me to watch it.

01:14:32.027 --> 01:14:32.293
I saw them with the cat-o'-nine-tails ripping His flesh off His body.

01:14:39.429 --> 01:14:39.777
And I saw the agony on His face as it was being ripped off of Him.

01:14:39.777 --> 01:14:43.160
I could see His bones.

01:14:43.160 --> 01:14:47.743
He allowed me to watch the whole thing.

01:14:47.743 --> 01:14:50.370
It was the most gruesome thing.

01:14:50.370 --> 01:14:52.800
He said, "What do you not understand?

01:14:53.760 --> 01:14:55.380
That by My stripes you were healed.

01:15:14.610 --> 01:15:17.760
I took it all for you.

01:15:17.760 --> 01:15:36.063
" He said, "The same faith that it takes for you to believe that you're born again is the same faith that it takes for you to be healed.

01:15:36.063 --> 01:15:53.303
" He said, "You don't realize you were once lost, but now you're found," and what it takes for you to be able to say that and the miracle that it truly is: to be so lost, but now you're found.

01:15:58.727 --> 01:15:59.133
I was blind, but now I see.

01:15:59.540 --> 01:16:11.560
You don't realize what I truly did for you by dying and suffering for you so that you don't have to kill a goat anymore.

01:16:11.560 --> 01:16:14.867
You don't have to kill a calf.

01:16:14.867 --> 01:16:18.707
I was the ultimate sacrifice for you.

01:16:18.707 --> 01:16:20.500
I became sin.

01:16:20.500 --> 01:16:22.780
I became sickness.

01:16:22.780 --> 01:16:27.160
I took it all for you.

01:16:30.560 --> 01:16:39.653
And you so flippantly say, "Lord, forgive me of my sins," and you don't even realize what you're truly saying.

01:16:45.069 --> 01:16:45.314
The wages of sin is death.

01:16:45.314 --> 01:16:46.310
Do you understand?

01:16:47.060 --> 01:16:48.880
The wages of sin is death.

01:17:03.582 --> 01:17:03.724
It leads you to hell.

01:17:03.724 --> 01:17:08.790
But Jesus paid the price for you to walk in victory over death, hell, and the grave.

01:17:08.790 --> 01:17:16.926
He whipped it all once and for all.

01:17:26.340 --> 01:17:26.600
It is finished.

01:17:26.600 --> 01:17:28.160
I took your sickness.

01:17:44.780 --> 01:17:45.125
I took your disease.

01:17:45.125 --> 01:17:47.000
I took your infirmities.

01:17:47.000 --> 01:17:48.120
I took poverty.

01:17:48.120 --> 01:17:54.027
He became poor that we might be rich through His poverty.

01:17:54.027 --> 01:18:00.320
God took it all for you to walk in victory.

01:18:00.900 --> 01:18:08.200
And He said, "You say it and you believe it, and you don't question it.

01:18:08.200 --> 01:18:09.740
I'm born again.

01:18:09.740 --> 01:18:18.190
I believe it, but you don't question it.

01:18:18.200 --> 01:18:22.594
" He said, "I took sickness the same way I took sin.

01:18:22.594 --> 01:18:25.109
By My stripes, you are healed.

01:18:25.109 --> 01:18:28.933
Either you believe it or you don't.

01:18:28.933 --> 01:18:32.742
" He said that I took the poverty for you.

01:18:53.920 --> 01:18:54.135
I took it.

01:18:54.350 --> 01:18:58.013
You don't have to be mentally poor.

01:19:03.585 --> 01:19:03.860
You don't have to have anguish and fear and anxiety.

01:19:17.080 --> 01:19:17.950
I took it all for you.

01:19:31.690 --> 01:19:31.865
He was wounded for our transgressions.

01:19:31.865 --> 01:19:34.070
He was bruised for our iniquities.

01:19:35.360 --> 01:19:40.411
The chastisement of our peace was upon Him, and with His stripes, we are healed.

01:19:40.411 --> 01:19:44.543
And that's what He said to me.

01:19:44.543 --> 01:19:52.935
He said, "Believe it like you believe in salvation, Brandon.

01:19:52.935 --> 01:20:06.840
" As I saw His flesh hanging off His body, as I could see His blood flowing so much that it was a pool of blood all around Him.

01:20:06.840 --> 01:20:16.775
Then He picked Himself up.

01:20:16.775 --> 01:20:27.903
They shoved that crown down on His head more and they ripped pieces of His beard out of His face.

01:20:36.093 --> 01:20:36.280
And He was in agonizing pain.

01:20:37.898 --> 01:20:38.707
I could see it.

01:20:38.707 --> 01:20:45.760
He didn't look human and He carried that cross and He died.

01:20:45.760 --> 01:20:58.228
He had humongous holes in His hands and His feet, and He did it all for you and for me.

01:20:58.228 --> 01:21:03.710
Then they pierced His side, and blood and water flowed.

01:21:03.710 --> 01:21:06.560
He said, "What more do you need?

01:21:06.560 --> 01:21:08.380
" That's what He asked me.

01:21:21.013 --> 01:21:21.307
"What more do you need to know?

01:21:31.307 --> 01:21:31.493
What more?

01:21:31.493 --> 01:21:32.144
What more do you need?

01:21:32.144 --> 01:21:35.260
I took it all for you.

01:21:35.260 --> 01:21:45.080
" Because I asked Him—He showed me all this—and then the question I had in my heart was, "What does it take to be healed?

01:21:45.080 --> 01:21:48.415
What does it take to walk in victory?

01:22:12.770 --> 01:22:13.035
" He said, "I took it all for you.

01:22:55.100 --> 01:22:55.355
